  <p>The key changes relate to the housing programmes. These have been revised in light of better information on the timing of spend and the amount required to meet our targets and in considering how best to use resources from slippage from last year. In doing so we have identified savings of &#163;35 million from the overall housing budget, which we have redirected at other Executive priorities. These changes will still allow us to meet all our existing commitments and targets and address additional housing budget pressures.</p>

